<plot>Rebecca and Amy are a pair of sexy young television reporters working for a respected "60 Minutes"-like newsmagazine. Receiving their story assignments from New York producer Francis Casey, the girls travel across the country in their specially equipped van solving crimes, reporting the news, and getting involved in the lives of others. Jason Cook was the host of the show, "The American Report".</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?540064</url></doc>
